Package org.openftc.revextensions2

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    VexMC29
    Support for the VEX Motor Controller 29 To use an MC29, connect it to a servo port, then on the Robot Controller or Driver Station, configure the port you connected it to as a VEX Motor Controller 29
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ExpansionHubEx
    Provides an implementation of the REV Expansion Hub's features that are not included in the standard FTC SDK.
    ExpansionHubMotor
    Extends a DcMotorImplEx to provide access to new features.
    ExpansionHubServo
    Extends a ServoImplEx to provide access to new features.
